hi-there-i-am-vanessa-marley.original: Hi there, I am Vanessa Marley

p-strong-photographer-strong-and-strong-.original: Photographer and Visual Content Strategist from Albany. I work as a lifestyle, product, and landscape photographer, creating images for a diverse range of requests, from online media to printed artwork.
p-strong-photographer-strong-and-strong-.value: Fotógrafo y estratega de contenido visual de Albany. Trabajo como fotógrafo de estilo de vida, productos y paisajes, creando imágenes para una amplia gama de solicitudes, desde medios digitales hasta obras impresas.
